title: NFL ATL: AFC playoff picture
itunes:title: NFL ATL: AFC playoff picture
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling break down the AFC playoff picture and catch up with New York Jets columnist Manish Mehta. Get caught up with the latest headlines from around the league and find out which unlucky team makes their debut on the ‘Stick a Fork’ segment. The crew also previews the Week 11 “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the Indianapolis Colts and Tennessee Titans. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
